{"tid":1350051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LingU仔全部同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:29:19.000Z","uid":121048,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d58b4f66afa79cbba2d13b0a76dbcdf65fdb16ec","tid":1350051,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"我知依架嶺事館嗰邊搞緊聯署，準備聲討何君堯條仆街校董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係要預咗學校方面或者何妖係唔會有咩實際行動，最多出篇聲名噏下廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地要諗定點樣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將行動升級</span><br />\n我有少少建議:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一: 全體學生罷交學費</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二: 圍堵校務處/校長宿舍</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三: 九月開學全校罷課</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四: NSO開學禮嘅時候，將dem cheer環節改為高呼口號</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五: 搞遊行&amp;連儂牆呢啲基本野</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LingU仔就算係八大之尾，但都要有骨氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嶺大之恥，恥與為伍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷免何君堯嶺大校董一職</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469385068ff39506350181bb19f217bbaccbc850","tid":1350051,"uid":121048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"